Hello! Thank you for calling Crescendo Music School, this is Timothy Brown Who do I have the pleasure of speaking with today?

Hi Timothy, this is Beverly Rogers. I have some questions about a shipment I was expecting.

Of course, Beverly. I'd be happy to help you with that. Could you provide me with the order number so I can look up your shipment details?

I don't have the order number on hand right now, which is why I'm a bit confused.

No worries, Beverly. Could you please provide me with your email address? That will help me locate your order in our system.

Sure, my email address is beverly.rogers@email.com.

Thank you, Beverly. I found your order. It looks like your shipment was scheduled for delivery yesterday, but there seems to be a delay. Could you also confirm your shipping address for verification?

Yes, it's one two three Music Lane, Suite B, Harmon Town.

Great, thank you for confirming that, Beverly. I see the package is now rescheduled for delivery tomorrow. I'm sorry for the confusion and delay.

I see, that clarifies things. I appreciate your help, Timothy.

Anytime, Beverly. Thank you for your patience, and please let us know if there's anything else we can assist you with. Have a wonderful day! Goodbye!
